{"tid":182601,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救)兔仔胃脹","createTime":"2017-04-01T12:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T06:44:07.000Z","uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee558aff899bcd1f7b8a0e706ebae319744b0870","tid":182601,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T12:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/a0nkcto1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa0nkcto1&h=6d77491a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人兔仔試過腸+胃脹?<br />\n睇獸醫之前可以點處理/幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f05d34b747a2ff88c6459e769cd5669bbba8c5","tid":182601,"uid":57635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:53:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/a0nkcto1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa0nkcto1&h=6d77491a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人兔仔試過腸+胃脹?<br />\n睇獸醫之前可以點處理/幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家情況點？<br />\n我個隻前排無啦啦又係咁<br />\n睇醫生前應該用熱毛巾敷肚"},{"pid":"3ee05db504c19416df106276f950c1926b2b57c3","tid":182601,"uid":65441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:57:15.000Z","msg":"help u pish"},{"pid":"bf3d63aa32b6eadfa0945313a28241d01b28de29","tid":182601,"uid":5716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:02:27.000Z","msg":"去買支兔毛膏喂俾佢食(用黎滑腸），千其唔好喂木瓜丸（食左會更賬）。順時針用陰力幫佢按肚，另外兔兔肯唔肯食草？情況唔嚴重或食得少喂草粉，唔多食野即刻立即馬上一定要去睇醫生，兔兔唔等得。"},{"pid":"594545d846239b07cfcfcb0a63266720013f13ab","tid":182601,"uid":38351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:44:07.000Z","msg":"餵草粉: 2-3 個鐘一次，脹成咁會唔肯食，一定要餵先得。<br />\n每半個鐘- 一個鐘按摩最少10分鐘。<br />\n按摩手法用掌心按下打圈，由內至外打圈，間中雙手按下由頭至尾向後掃。<br />\n肚脹可以無原因，特別轉季嗰陣最易發。<br />\n記得儘快睇醫生，推薦毛國界。醫生會開促進腸胃藥，止痛藥。"}]}